2004-06-11  Rhys Weatherley  <rweather@southern-storm.com.au>

	* doc/libjit.texi, jit/jit-insn.c, jit/jit-internal.h,
	jit/jit-reg-alloc.c, jit/jit-rules-arm.c, jit/jit-rules-arm.sel,
